                                                <h3 class="gdlr-core-title-item-title gdlr-core-skin-title " style="font-size: 27px ;font-weight: 600 ;letter-spacing: 0px ;text-transform: none ;">Uganda Signs MoU with UAE to Ease Labour Export</h3>
                                                
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="comment-time kingster-info-font">
                                            <a href="index-2.html#comment-7">
                                                <time datetime="2016-11-26T15:04:44+00:00"> <h6><i class="fa fa-calendar"> Posted on July 9,2019 </i> <i class="fa fa-user"> Admin</i></h6> </time>
                                            </a>
